<div class="title">Dosage Experiment</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. peruvianus</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=The+Caveman&Exact=1">The Caveman</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; The Caveman. "Dosage Experiment: An Experience with Cacti - T. peruvianus (exp8263)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 29, 2004. erowid.org/exp/8263</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

